high_descs: Turn around and go to the shelf next to the bed.

Turn around to go out of the door into the kitchen straight across the sink.
Put the spatula in the sink, turn on the water to rinse it off, and take the spatula out.
Turn right and then left and then left into the living room and stand between the couch and the diningtable.
Put the spatula on the dining table in the upper left-hand corner.
